Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.45,0:05:01.36,op-cn,,0,0,0,,“U R MY SPECIAL”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.58,0:05:09.58,op-cn,,0,0,0,,“U R MY SPECIAL”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.99,0:05:17.80,op-cn,,0,0,0,,“U R MY SPECIAL”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:22.13,op-cn,,0,0,0,,在弥留之际起舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.13,0:05:25.97,op-cn,,0,0,0,,东京前线 尽兴之都
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.97,0:05:30.35,op-cn,,0,0,0,,在生死之间挣扎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:34.77,op-cn,,0,0,0,,展现你不拘小节的面孔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:36.93,op-cn,,0,0,0,,“i luv u 6a6y”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.93,0:05:39.07,op-cn,,0,0,0,,不停歌唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.07,0:05:43.11,op-cn,,0,0,0,,不论多么愚蠢 不论多么陌生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.11,0:05:47.22,op-cn,,0,0,0,,都在举手投足间 燃烧内心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:48.79,op-cn,,0,0,0,,开始奔跑 便失去控制
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.79,0:05:50.62,op-cn,,0,0,0,,“U R MY SPECIAL”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:54.91,op-cn,,0,0,0,,能否将我彻底蹂躏？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.91,0:05:58.80,op-cn,,0,0,0,,尽情吞食我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.80,0:06:03.13,op-cn,,0,0,0,,回游于迷宫 幽会一生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:07.01,op-cn,,0,0,0,,令我眼花缭乱 “U R MY SPECIAL”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:11.37,op-cn,,0,0,0,,暧昧不清的世界 旋转不停
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:15.19,op-cn,,0,0,0,,No!No!No! 不要如此冷静
